 and useful stuff comes out of it, but most of the steps along the way are mainly of interests to other specialists.&nbsp;</p><p>Having said that, I'm not sure how much of this applies to EA, apart from the highly technical stuff. A lot of it is intended to guide a general audience, so i see the appeal in aiming towards said audience.</p>", "parentCommentId": "eSkZFkPgwvSLJPu2G", "user": {"username": "titotal"}}]